<item>
            <title>[SPR-225] build process doesn&apos;t include spring.vm for Velocity macros</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-225</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I checked out the latest code from CVS tonight in order to use the new Velocity macros for forms.  I found that spring.vm wasn&apos;t include in the created JAR, and therefore the macros didn&apos;t work.  Modifying build.xml fixed the problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll try to attach a patch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="10422">SPR-225</key>
            <summary>build process doesn&apos;t include spring.vm for Velocity macros</summary>
