                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="10638" author="mraible" created="Sun, 18 Jul 2004 18:37:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to include Velocity macros.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="10651" author="mraible" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2004 00:25:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The build process doesn&apos;t include *&lt;b&gt;/&lt;/b&gt;.ftl either.  This is needed for including the FreeMarker templates.  Below is a modified XML that&apos;s needed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;copy todir=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{target.classes.dir}
&lt;p&gt;&quot; preservelastmodified=&quot;true&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;fileset dir=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{src.dir}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;include name=&quot;*&lt;b&gt;/&lt;/b&gt;.xml&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;include name=&quot;*&lt;b&gt;/&lt;/b&gt;.dtd&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;include name=&quot;*&lt;b&gt;/&lt;/b&gt;.vm&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;include name=&quot;*&lt;b&gt;/&lt;/b&gt;.ftl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/fileset&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/copy&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    </comments>
